00:11:57,200 --> 00:12:01,580
♫The soulmates parted ways♫

168
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:04,330
She is Su Xiao Wei.
(A warm welcome to Caring Enterprise)

169
00:12:04,410 --> 00:12:07,410
When she was 6 years old,
she lost her parents...

170
00:12:07,970 --> 00:12:09,270
in a road accident.

171
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:13,100
She injured her eyes in the accident.

172
00:12:14,190 --> 00:12:16,630
Afterwards,
she was sent to the welfare home.

173
00:12:17,290 --> 00:12:19,950
Though she's lost her parents,

174
00:12:20,630 --> 00:12:23,790
the warmth from the society...

175
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:25,980
has made her happy again.

176
00:12:26,610 --> 00:12:29,150
Xiao Wei is currently in Year Three.

177
00:12:29,970 --> 00:12:32,830
She's received lots of attention
and love from her teachers.

178
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:34,990
Look.

179
00:12:35,070 --> 00:12:37,690
Her class teachers are over there.

180
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:40,950
Well...

