Xiao Wei, you must be exhausted.

190
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,400
You did a great job.

191
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:50,480
You performed sign language
and singing at once.

192
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:52,000
Did you know?

193
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,960
Mr Su was clapping for you all the time.

194
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,370
Thank you.

195
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,190
Where is Mr Su?

196
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:01,610
Has he left?

197
