245
00:18:08,860 --> 00:18:10,360
I'm still at the museum.

246
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,260
It's too remote. I can't get a ride.

247
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:18,260
Send me your location.
I'll get a ride for you.

248
